title: [Coastal Cliffs]
description: The cliffs narrow and you catch a glimpse of the jagged, rocky wasteland that lies eighty or so feet below you.  A few small rocks tumble out over the edge,  and it is breathless moments later before you hear them smash against the boulders below.
